  "remarks": "Sergei Gorbunov is the Deputy Head of the Executive Committee of the All-Russia People’s Front. In this role, he is responsible for the organisation and execution of the campaign “Everything for Victory!” which aims to support military units in the so-called “Donetsk People’s Republic” and “Luhansk People’s Republic” with items necessary for military operations. He is directly responsible for providing means to the fighters in those regions.",
